## Directus Deployment Information

- **App ID**: `106f3fa1-b968-41f4-b474-80262cdd1a44`
- **URL**: `https://directus.allisons.dev` (Custom domain)
- **Default URL**: `https://allisons-portfolio-directus-9vxdi.ondigitalocean.app`
- **Region**: `nyc`
- **Directus Version**: `11.5.1`
- **HTTP Port**: `8055`
- **Instance Size**: `basic-xs`

