## Directus Management

For Directus management, use the following commands:

```bash
# Get Directus app details
doctl apps get 106f3fa1-b968-41f4-b474-80262cdd1a44

# Check Directus logs
doctl apps logs 106f3fa1-b968-41f4-b474-80262cdd1a44 --follow=false | grep -i "error"

# Create new deployment
doctl apps create-deployment 106f3fa1-b968-41f4-b474-80262cdd1a44 --wait
```

## Development Preferences

- Always use the composables for data fetching
- Add proper error handling and data validation
- Implement defensive programming when accessing API data
- Test API endpoints directly when troubleshooting 